I think Yanshosh deserves a round of applause, he's finally put the polls up!!

These polls work through eGroups, so to vote, you need to login at 
http://egroups.com/login.cgi and then go on to 
http://www.egroups.com/polls/nbwrpg or just follow the links.

If you don't know, or don't remember your password, click "Forgot Password?" 
(down near the bottom of http://egroups.com/login.cgi), and follow the 
instructions.

Voting is fun, and the more votes we get, the better. So VOTE!!! Have a great 
day, everyone!

P.S. You must be at least 18 months to vote. I think we all qualify.
